- Too late!

47
00:07:11,164 --> 00:07:13,792
- Don't bust my ass!
- Fuck off!

48
00:07:13,900 --> 00:07:16,198
- Come on, drop it!
- No!

49
00:07:16,302 --> 00:07:17,701
