63
00:09:29,835 --> 00:09:34,704
To him, it proves man
descends from animals.

64
00:09:35,841 --> 00:09:38,867
He once had a tail...

65
00:09:39,912 --> 00:09:42,608
now it's gone.

66
00:09:43,783 --> 00:09:46,650
Yet, he keeps shaking his ass...

67
00:09:49,288 --> 00:09:51,779
